Package: metaMultiverse
Type: Package
Title: Multiverse Meta-Analysis Toolkit
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Constantin Yves Plessen <yves.plessen@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Constantin Yves Plessen <yves.plessen@gmail.com>
Description: A toolkit for conducting multiverse meta-analysis, with functions for generating specification grids, performing various estimation methods (PET-PEESE, P-uniform, UWLS, WAAP), and visualizing results using both static and interactive plots. Implements the E/U/N decision type framework for principled multiverse analysis. Designed for researchers and data scientists working with meta-analytic methods.
VignetteBuilder: knitr
